**sorTA CHANGELOG**

____________________
# Version: 1.4.1
# Date: November , 2018


#   Updates
+ 	Adding Config JSON for saving Shows 
+	Fixed regular expression (Flag error)
+	Added Logo for -p
+	Added colour variables
+	Using realpath, fixed some issues when in certain directories
+	Added SET & GET methods for movie locations (Win/Unix)
+	Show List, Add Shows and check if show is added.
+	Added -p check for when queueing episodes (uses -p for directory chose)
+	Seasons beginning with zero is removed (01,02,03...etc)
+	Updated match and groups for new regexp

#   Backlog ToDo
+ 	Use Lists instead of Strings for: extensions_regexp1
+ 	BBC.Show --> Bbc Show Folder | Fix to Upper
+ 	Clean titles, easy to implement, check f and remove junk between S01E05(.*).mp4
+	When sorted, give option to export file with moved files and output console
____________________
# Version: 1.4
# Date: November , 2018


#   Updates
+ 	Adding Config JSON on next build, for saving Shows 
+ 	Specify correct Show e.g mitm.s01e01 should go into folder 'Movie In The Moon'
	sorta.py -s "mitm:Movie In The Moon"
+	RegExp changes, still flagging, added ToDo
+	Bump to 1.4
+	Updated Logo
+	Changed parser... - for one letter, -- for greater the 2 letters
+	Experiment with colors

#   Backlog ToDo
